{
  "id": "adv_event_2109_01_03",
  "title": "合宿スタート",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後。すずの別荘",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later‚ at Suzu’s holiday villa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.8399999618530272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3……愛、手足の動きがバラバラよ！\nちゃんと私と合わせなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3… Ai‚ your hand and foot movements are out of sync!\nFollow me properly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.933333333333333,
      "endTime": 9.533333333333331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい！　すみません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-okay! I’m sorry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.833333333333334,
      "endTime": 12.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 9.833333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 12.766666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "愛！　もっと背筋を伸ばして、堂々と踊りなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai! Straighten your back more‚ and dance with more confidence!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.766666666666667,
      "endTime": 16.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 17.066666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "さっきから愛は叱られてばかりですわね\n莉央さんの指導はいつもこんなに厳しいのですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai has been getting scolded non-stop for a while.\nIs Rio-san’s instruction always this strict?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.066666666666666,
      "endTime": 24.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、莉央さんが厳しいって言うより\n今日は愛ちゃんが酷過ぎかな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well. More than Rio-san being strict‚\ntoday it’s Ai-chan being terrible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.066666666666666,
      "endTime": 31.633333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 25.0666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 31.866666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんとの関係がギクシャクし始めてから\n調子を崩しているそうですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since her relationship with Rio-san started to get strained‚\nher condition has been worsening.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.866666666666667,
      "endTime": 37.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ここは私の力で愛と莉央さんの仲を\n取り持って差し上げますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I shall help sort out the relationship\nbetween Ai and Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.06666666666667,
      "endTime": 43.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "そこで、さっそくすずにゃんにやってほしいことが\nあるんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And on that topic‚ there’s just something I want you to do\nfor me right away‚ Suzu-nyan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.86666666666667,
      "endTime": 48.7139009197553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 43.8666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 49.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、練習お疲れ様でした\n夕食まではリビングでくつろいでくださいまし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve all been practicing hard.\nYou should relax in the dining room until dinner time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.833333333333336,
      "endTime": 57.900000000000006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 58.166666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば合宿中は誰がごはんを作るんですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ who’s going to cook the meals for this camp?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.166666666666664,
      "endTime": 63.30342384974161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "そのことですが、今から全員でくじ引きをして\n料理当番を二人決めさせていただきますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to do a lottery to decide\nwhich two of us will be in charge of the cooking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5,
      "endTime": 70.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 70.5333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "一体料理当番が誰になるのか……\n一切不正のないこのくじを全員で引くのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who will be the cooks‚ I wonder…\nI want everyone to pick one of these totally honest tickets!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 78.36973368326825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 78.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "その前に、くじ引きに仕掛けがないか\n確認してもいいかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before that‚ would you mind if I check to see that\nthe tickets haven’t been fixed?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.73333333333333,
      "endTime": 83.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6,
      "endTime": 84.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 83.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "ふ、ふふふふ不正なんて、あああるはずありませんわ！\nくくくじに仕掛けなんて全然ありませんわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha‚ of course they’re n-not f-fixed! The very idea!\nThere’s absolutely no t-t-trickery with the tickets!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.73333333333333,
      "endTime": 92.43087972005209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 92.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "めちゃくちゃ動揺してる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s shaking all over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.73333333333333,
      "endTime": 94.85795918305715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 95.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "図星だったみたいね\nイカサマをするなんて、すずは何が目的なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I seem to have been right on the mark.\nWhat are you trying to pull‚ Suzu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 100.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 101.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "目的だなんて、私は、その……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not trying to pull anything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.16666666666667,
      "endTime": 105.86666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 106.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんは壊滅的に料理が下手なんですよ\nだから料理したくなくて小細工したんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu is terrifyingly bad at cooking.\nThat’s why you didn’t want to cook and rigged it‚ am I right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.23333333333333,
      "endTime": 112.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう私は料理が壊滅的に……なんですって！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I am terrifyingly bad at coo… what did you say!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.66666666666667,
      "endTime": 117.23333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 117.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "そ・う・だ・よ・ね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Am? I? Right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6,
      "endTime": 120.46814050674438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "うう……そ、その通りですわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Er‚ yes‚ just like you say…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.66666666666667,
      "endTime": 125.53333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 120.666666666667
    },
