      "text": "私がレッスンに集中出来ない理由は\nそれだけじゃないよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not the only reason why I can’t\nconcentrate on lessons…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262,
      "endTime": 266.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
