      "text": "でも、私なんかがそんなことを言ったら\nきっと莉央さんが気を悪くするでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if I said something like that‚\nit would only upset Rio-san‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 275.7,
      "endTime": 282.3666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
